    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>The mention of summer romance struck a note with me. I was about to say I never had a summer romance &#8211; but I realize that I had several, one I will never forget.  It was in a book I read called SEVENTEENTH SUMMER  and,  while I was reading it, I was the heroine.  I still feel like I lived that summer.  </p>
<p>I had a few summers when I had a boyfriend,  and we did summery things together, but no big romance. My big romance happened in the fall, and another in the winter. But the most vivid one was Seventeenth Summer.</p>
<p>LindaC</p>
